Package: angstromATE
Type: Package
Title: Imports Recipe and Log Files from Angstrom Engineering Thermal Evaporator
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Thomas Gredig [aut, cre, cph] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5824-7626>)
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Gredig", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "tgredig@csulb.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5824-7626"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <tgredig@csulb.edu>
Description: Package for importing recipe and log files generated by Angstrom Engineering thermal evaporator systems. These recipe and log files contain detailed time-series records of chamber pressure, source activity, deposition rate, film thickness, tooling parameters, substrate conditions, and other process variables. `angstromATE` extracts the most useful information from these files and returns it in a compact, analysis-ready format.
License: GPL (>= 3) 
BugReports: https://github.com/thomasgredig/angstromATE/issues
